til - 'til - 'til I came home with the grub. And - and - the - the next day. What I got - what I got - yesterday - would be today's grub, see, so we'd - hot it up when we - when we come home - home from school. And have our grub when we - when I come home
 from school. See. That did for ten of us, yes.
