\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13239045 WT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4005851\charrsid16151298 No, no, no, no, she'd - she'd - she'd give you as much as she could without - oh yes, she had to be careful, you - the - the polic
e stop - stopped me once. He said - outside the Great Central Hotel, he - he sto}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516132\charrsid16151298 p}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4005851\charrsid16151298 
ped me and asked me what I'd got in the bag. And I told - I told - told - I told him - told him I'd got - got - got - I'd got coal. He said, oh well, wher}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9516132\charrsid16151298 e}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
